# Line-ending normalization. Pairs with .editorconfig (see CONTRIBUTING.md).
# The repo is Windows-authored but CI builds/tests on Linux, so keep one
# canonical form: text files are stored with LF in the repo and checked out
# with the platform-native ending. Git auto-detects text vs. binary here.
* text=auto

# Binary assets tracked in this repo — never normalize or diff as text.
# (Imported audio/images live under %LocalAppData%, not git, so no rules for them.)
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.webp binary
*.ico  binary
